{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_50","type":"agent_message","text":"The decompilation clarified the remaining bug: Plexus falls back to `java.lang.Object` when it can’t load the implementation class from `components.xml`. In this version’s test, `DefaultMavenProjectBuilder` is only reached through the `MavenProjectBuilder` interface, so the current self-conditioned entry is too late; I’m changing that condition to the interface that’s actually reached before lookup."}}
